     ----------------------- && -----------------------

After the office, Brother Oswald confronts you. "Where was your mind, Brother Novice? Part of your duty is participating in offices."

For violating a serious rule of the priory, you are sentenced to bread and water for three days. By the time your penance ends, any chance of solving any mystery has long passed.

*** THIS WOULD KILL YOU, BUT NOT DURING DEBUGGING/PLAYTESTING.


