You continue to sing with the others.

> WAIT 30 MINUTES
Time passes.

> X FLUFF
Looking more closely, it looks like fur from the orange cat.

You continue to sing with the others.

> TAKE FLUFF
First, you'd need to get up from the stalls.

     ----------------------- && -----------------------

The office ends.

Brother Aelred touches your shoulder. "Son, take your time here. When you're done, come meet me in the gardens."

You spend several minutes reflecting on your life now: ritual, timing, prayer, silence. It feels both comforting and confining. You're not sure which feeling prevails.


